roxappletbuilder - applets for rox filer panel + framework

1) Content
2) Installation
3) Contact

---------------------------------------------------------------------
Content

This project consists of a framework for implementing rox filer applets and
some demo applets.

The framework can be found below the 'framework' directory. The applets are
located in the 'applets' directory.

---------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation

Before you can use the rox filer applets you have to install the
roxappletbuilder framework. To install the framework check out the file
framework/README.

Installation instructions for the applets can be found in the applet
directories.

